  <p>A fast-growing energy company builds linear generators—machines that generate electricity from linear motion, using hydrogen, ammonia, biogas—almost any fuel.</p>
  <p>Amazing tech. But there’s a problem.</p>
  <p>Energy infrastructure is changing faster than policy can keep up. Power sources are becoming decentralized. Grids are growing brittle. To stay ahead, they knew they needed machine learning solutions. For that they needed an ML platform. And it needed to be theirs.</p>
  <p>They had to own it.</p>

